  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This research is aimed at verifying the effects of diets with high protein and low glycemic
      index (GI) on weight management among overweight or obese Chinese adult. Additionally, the
      investigators intend to verify the effects of two new approaches, including food replacement
      and Internet-of-things (IOT) monitoring on weight control.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
